data.description: Luxury living on 1 level, no HOA, and sits on almost 2 acres of land!! Totally updated and better than new!! This charming home was built in 1971 and offers over 3000 square feet on 1 level of easy maintenance free living. This home seamlessly blends vintage character with modern elegance. Featuring updated interior and exterior, contemporary amenities and well thought out modern designs. This home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, dual living areas and 2 owner suites!! This home has so much to offer and it is just waiting on a new owner!! Call today for your private showing!!
